{"id": "art-82", "label": "Art. 82", "title": "Art. 82: Anularea şi efectele renunţării la aplicarea pedepsei", "slug": "art-82", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1203428324\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1436\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1203428324\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 82: Anularea\n&#351;i efectele renun&#355;&#259;rii la aplicarea pedepsei </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_172968375\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1435\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_172968375\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Persoana fa&#355;&#259; de care s-a dispus\nrenun&#355;area la aplicarea pedepsei nu este supus&#259; niciunei\ndec&#259;deri, interdic&#355;ii sau incapacit&#259;&#355;i ce ar putea decurge\ndin infrac&#355;iunea s&#259;vâr&#351;it&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2095761767\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1434\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2095761767\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Renun&#355;area la aplicarea pedepsei nu produce efecte\nasupra execut&#259;rii m&#259;surilor de siguran&#355;&#259; &#351;i a\nobliga&#355;iilor civile prev&#259;zute în hot&#259;râre.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1292235835\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1433\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1292235835\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; în termen de 2 ani de la r&#259;mânerea\ndefinitiv&#259; a hot&#259;rârii prin care s-a dispus renun&#355;area la\naplicarea pedepsei se descoper&#259; c&#259; persoana fa&#355;&#259; de care\ns-a luat aceast&#259; m&#259;sur&#259; s&#259;vâr&#351;ise anterior\nr&#259;mânerii definitive a hot&#259;rârii o alt&#259; infrac&#355;iune, pentru\ncare i s-a stabilit o pedeaps&#259; chiar dup&#259; expirarea acestui termen,\nrenun&#355;area la aplicarea pedepsei se anuleaz&#259; &#351;i se stabile&#351;te\npedeapsa pentru infrac&#355;iunea care a atras ini&#355;ial renun&#355;area la\naplicarea pedepsei, aplicându-se apoi, dup&#259; caz, dispozi&#355;iile\nprivitoare la concursul de infrac&#355;iuni, recidiv&#259; sau pluralitate\nintermediar&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 4:Amânarea aplic&#259;rii\npedepsei</span></b></p>"}